Oran claims for infringement of its UK registered trade mark number 3021545 for the mark ORAN PRE-CAST (“the Registered Mark”) in respect of the Defendants’ use of the signs ORANMORE PRE-CAST / ORANMORE PRECAST / ORANMORE (in the form of the internet domain 
		www.oranmore.co.uk
	      ) (the “ORANMORE Signs”) both with and without the First Defendant’s Device (set out in Annex 1 to this judgment). Oran applied for the Registered Mark on 11 September 2013 and it was registered on 6 December 2013. The trade mark infringement claim therefore relates only to Oranmore’s trade after 6 December 2013.

